 offers an innovative understanding of a tumultuous time of decolonization.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aCommodificationzFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aFeminine beauty (Aesthetics)xEconomic aspectszFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aFemininityxEconomic aspectszFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aNational characteristics, FrenchxHistoryy20th century. 0aTourismzFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aWomenzFrancexHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / Europe / France.2bisacsh  aAir France.  aBrigitte Bardot.  aEurope.  aFrench history.  aFrench tourism.  aOlympic hostess.  aair hostess.  agender.  ahostess fashions.  apostwar France.  aromantic.  asoft power.  astewardess.  awomen’s history.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311127195808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2023 Englishz978311131913108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2023z9783111318189oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311079736740uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978148753808840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781487538088423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781487538088/original  a978-3-11-079736-7  University of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-127195-8  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-131913-1  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_EMB  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZD